thread.title: BRIEF-Queclink Wireless Solutions sees Q1 2018 net profit down 10 pct to 39.9 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Queclink Wireless Solutions sees Q1 2018 net profit down 10 pct to 39.9 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - queclink wireless solutions co ltd

text:
Feb 28(Reuters) - Queclink Wireless Solutions Co Ltd
* Sees Q1 2018 net profit to decrease by 10 percent to 39.9 percent, or to be 10.4 million yuan to 15.6 million yuan
* Says Q1 2017 net profit was 17.3 million yuan
* Says that increased sales income, increased costs and exchange loss as main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/ZfhQXe
